headline: Truist Raises The Home Depot, Inc. (HD) Price Target to $405, Reiterates Buy
summary: We recently published an article titled 9 Best Lumber Stocks to Invest in Now. The Home Depot, Inc. (NYSE:HD) is among the best lumber stocks to invest in now.
